omm_input_uri_query: SELECT Artifact.uri FROM caom2.Artifact AS Artifact JOIN caom2.Plane AS Plane ON Artifact.planeID = Plane.planeID JOIN caom2.Observation AS Observation ON Plane.obsID = Observation.obsID WHERE Observation.collection = 'OMM' AND Artifact.uri not like '%jpg' AND Artifact.uri like 'ad:OMM/%' AND Observation.lastModified < '2018-07-01 00:00:00.000' LIMIT 10
